        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ".—He then passes on to the various plagues threatened in the Law—famine, pestilence, blasting of the corn, mildew on the fruit, locust and caterpillar (see ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
